<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Welcome back to XYZ Hospital</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 40px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .message {
        width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .signature {
        text-align: right;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .signature p {
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
      .signature img {
        width: 100px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="message">
      <h1>Welcome back to XYZ Hospital</h1>
      <p>Dear [patient name],</p>
      <p>
        We are glad to see you back at XYZ Hospital. We hope you are feeling
        better and have fully recovered from your medical condition. Our team of
        doctors and nurses is here to provide you with the best possible care
        and support during your stay with us.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns during your stay, please do not
        hesitate to contact our staff. We are here to ensure that your
        experience with us is as comfortable and stress-free as possible.
      </p>
      <p>
        Thank you for choosing XYZ Hospital for your healthcare needs. We wish
        you a speedy recovery and hope to see you back on your feet soon.
      </p>
      <div class="signature">
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <img src="hospital_logo.png" alt="Hospital Logo" />
        <p>XYZ Hospital Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
